flowchart TD

User[User Natural Language Question]

User
    → APIGW[API Gateway]

APIGW
    → Orchestrator[Lambda Chat Orchestrator]

Orchestrator
    → Session[DynamoDB Session Store]

Orchestrator
    → ContextBuilder[Context Builder]

ContextBuilder
    → DatasetCatalog[Dataset Catalog Loader]

DatasetCatalog
    → Planner

ContextBuilder
    → Planner[LLM Planner]

Planner
    → QuerySpec[QuerySpec JSON]

QuerySpec
    → Validator[QuerySpec Validator]

Validator
    → Resolver[Dataset Resolver]

Resolver
    → SQLBuilder[SQL Builder AST]

SQLBuilder
    → DB[(Aurora PostgreSQL Read Replica)]

DB
    → Formatter[Response Formatter]

Formatter
    → Response[Final Response]

Response
    → Orchestrator

Orchestrator
    → SaveSession[Update Session]

SaveSession
    → UserResponse[Return to User]
